      "value": "ab 1164 Markgraf, ab 1180 Herzog der Steiermark"
    },
    "en": {
      "language": "en",
      "value": "Margrave of Styria from 1164 and Duke from 1180, when Styria, previously a margraviate subordinated to the stem duchy of Bavaria, was raised to the status of an independent duchy"
    },
